  Npc_SouthHateru006_AreaOut_01:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: animation
          name: Greeting_00
      - text: 哎呀～你要去哪？
  Npc_SouthHateru006_AreaOut_02:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "要是你跑太遠的話，\n就不知道正確時間了，\n所以可以請你\n別離這間驛站太遠嗎？"
  Npc_SouthHateru006_H_Near000:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - text: 隨時都等著你喔。
  Talk_01:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "因為馬是野生的，不容易馴服，\n但當你擁有自己的馬，世界就會變得不一樣喔！\n畢竟我可是「野生馬匹馴服錦標賽」的亞軍，\n相信我說的準沒錯！"
  Talk_03:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "這一帶是野生馬匹的寶庫！\n不管帶什麼馬過來都行。"
  Talk_04:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "我的紀錄是「2分鐘」，\n請在2分鐘內把野生馬匹帶來這裡，\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 0
      - text: 那要開始囉！
  Talk_05:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "因為野生馬匹非常膽小，\n所以要悄～悄地靠近才行喔。"
  Talk_06:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 0
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 125
      - text: 太精彩了！
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 100
      - text: "不過……沒想到你居然這麼輕易\n就打破2分鐘的大關了……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "算了，雖說是「野生馬匹馴服錦標賽」的亞軍，\n但參賽選手只有我和我哥兩人而已……\n這是「第二屆野生馬匹馴服錦標賽」的優勝獎金！\n請收下吧！"
  Talk_07:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 10
      - text: "哈哈哈。\n2分鐘的大關比想像中還難打破吧？\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "就算我身為「野生馬匹馴服錦標賽」的亞軍，\n也花了好幾年才打破這個時間……\n你可千萬別氣餒喔。"
  Talk_08:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "還想再挑戰2分鐘的大關嗎？\n還是有其他的事呢？"
      - control:
          kind: choice
          choice_labels:
            - 5
            - 6
            - 7
            - 8
          selected_index: 0
          cancel_index: 3
          unknown: 10
  Talk_09:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 6
            - 2
      - text: 好了，時間到～
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n哎呀～差一點就成功了呢～"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
  Talk_10:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "哎呀～怎麼回事？\n你那不可置信的態度！\n……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: ……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 0
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 125
      - text: 好吧！
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 100
      - text: "\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "既然你不相信的話，\n\n要不要來挑戰弗撒蘭我這\n「野生馬匹馴服錦標賽」亞軍的紀錄啊？"
      - control:
          kind: choice
          choice_labels:
            - 3
            - 4
          selected_index: 0
          cancel_index: 1
          unknown: 6
  Talk_11:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 4
            - 0
      - text: "什麼……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 10
            - 0
      - text: "你說什麼！\n\n居然拒絕跟弗撒蘭我一較高下……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "不過……算了……\n這也沒辦法。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 0
      - text: "畢竟我可是「野生馬匹馴服錦標賽」的亞軍，\n你會怕也是很正常的！\n但弗撒蘭我不會逃避也不會躲藏！\n等你有自信時，再來一決勝負吧！"
  Talk_12:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 0
      - text: "這樣才對嘛！\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "規則很簡單，\n在時間內將野生馬匹帶來這裡就行了！"
  Talk_13:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 0
      - text: "哎呀～客人你下定決心了嗎？\n還是有其他的事呢？"
