      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "規則很簡單，\n在時間內將野生馬匹帶來這裡就行了！\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 1
      - text: 那要開始囉！
  Talk_22:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 11
      - text: 世界果然很大呢！
  Talk_TimerCK_001:
    attributes: Npc_SouthHateru006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 10
            - 21
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 125
      - text: 怎、怎麼可能！
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 100
      - text: "\n\n這麼短的時間……聽都沒聽過。\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "我這「野生馬匹馴服錦標賽」亞軍的紀錄，\n居然這麼輕易就被打破了……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 算了，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n其實參賽選手只有我和我哥兩人而已……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: longer
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 7
            - 0
      - text: "總之你讓我相當佩服！\n看來我還得多多修行才行呢！\n這是「第二屆野生馬匹馴服錦標賽」的優勝獎金！\n請收下吧！"
